root: ^"Eh? But I don't see you anywhere..."
^"No silly! I'm here! Inside your head!"
^"When spirit makes a contract with someone, they will resonate with their soul! Connecting us to your mind!"
^"Well, it's gonna take a while get used hearing voices in my head."
^"You can make use of my wind to climb up there. Just focus my power on your legs and see how it goes!"
^Through the power of the wind, you can now press 'Space' in midair to perform a 2nd jump!
